- **Stock**: S&P 500 (^GSPC)
- **Episode 0 Profit**: -$100.27
- **Episode 1**: Interrupted as per instruction.

> [!NOTE]
> A negative profit in the first episode is expected as the reinforcement learning agent starts with random exploration.

